ify;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 14pt;">+ The activity</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 14pt;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700;">E.g.</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>The man is writing an email.</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 14pt;">+ The general situation</span></p></div></div></div>')
