 700; font-size: inherit !important;">absolutely</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>fabulous<br style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;"><br style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;">- They can also modify other adverbs</strong><br style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;">Examples:</em><br style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;">She played the violin<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;">extremely</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>well.<br style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;">You''re speaking<strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;"><span>&nbsp;</span>too<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>quietly.</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; background-color: rgb(248, 202, 198);"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;">2. Form of adverbs</strong></span><br style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;"></span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(236, 202, 250); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-heig