tant; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;">Uncountable nouns<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>are nouns that come in a state or quantity which is impossible to count; liquids are uncountable, as are things that act like liquids (sand, air). They are always considered to be singular, and can be used with some, any, a little, and much.</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><em style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;"><u style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;">Example:</u></em><span>&nbsp;</span>intelligence, information, etc.</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(248, 202, 198);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;">5. Proper nouns &amp; Common nouns</strong></span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;">-<strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;"><span>&nbsp;</span>Proper noun</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>is a specific name of a person, place, or thing, and is always capitalized.</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;">Example:&nbsp;</em></strong>Does Helen have much homework to do this evening?&nbsp;⇒&nbsp;Helen is&nbsp;the name of a specific person</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;">-<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;">Common noun</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>is the generic name of an item in a class or group and is not capitalized unless appearing at the beginning of a sentence or in a title.</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;">Example:</em></strong><em style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;"><span>&nbsp;</span></em>The boy crossed the river. ⇒ Girl is a common noun; we do not learn the identity of the girl by reading this sentence, though we know the action she takes. River is also a common noun in this sentence.</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">+</span></em><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><em style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;"><span>&nbsp;</span></em><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Types of common nouns:</span>&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span></span></p><ul style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><li style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;">Concrete noun<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>is something that is perceived by the senses; something that is physical or real.</span></span></span></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin-left: 48px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;">Example:</em></strong><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;"><span>&nbsp;</span></strong>I heard the doorbell ⇒ Doorbell is a real thing that can be sensed.</span></span></span></p><ul style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><li style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;">Abstract noun</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>is something that cannot be perceived by the senses.</span></span></span></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin-left: 48px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 11px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: 18px;"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit !important;"><em style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important;">Example:<span>&nbsp;</span></em></strong>We can’t imagine the courage it took to do that ⇒ Courage is an abstract noun. Courage can’t be seen, heard, or sensed in any other way, but we know it exists.</span></span></span></p><ul style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: SVN-Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><li style=